snippet.textDisplay:
My Roasts:
0:35 his Tesla is a very boring shade of red and those ugly silver wheels look like they cost $5. And how dare he sell his legendary S2k when he should have built & boosted it
1:10 Perfect car but the wheels need to be spaced out a bit more in order to get "that fitment", I bet it's not as fast as it looks
1:55 when you decide to build an ugly turbo system instead of going with Fast Intentions, he's making at least 200 less whp than he could be making, then you can't even mount your hood
2:39 The red is fine on this car, but those wheels. It needs to be lowered on race suspension with the wheels spaced out. The chrome wheels look fine but are heavy and boring-shaped.
3:30 That green is unfitting and ugly, plus the nose has a bunch of empty space in the middle. But Murci is an amazing Lambo car.
4:32 This car looks like your neighbor's rusty shitbox to a normal non-car person. Headlights look old and faded. The wheels are your "mainstream JDM choice" and would look far better on Enkei RS05RR or something similar. This car is the true Godzilla, make it look like it too.
4:45 All that front splitter but no wing? So at high speeds it is constantly nose-diving? Still looks like an amazing and fast car...
5:54 The butt of the car is too stubby and short to look aesthetic. Also I can see your wheels are sunk in, again with the spacers! Smh. Good choice with the black wheels though.
6:30 I can already imagine Doug talking over his car and spitting all over the paint while doing it. Lower the car and get rid of those silver wheels.
7:10 Something is wrong with those rear wheels placement and the rear wing. The shape is just out of place. Is the rear bumper missing? And wash it please...
snippet.textOriginal:
*My Roasts:*
0:35 his Tesla is a very boring shade of red and those ugly silver wheels look like they cost $5. And how dare he sell his legendary S2k when he should have built & boosted it
1:10 Perfect car but the wheels need to be spaced out a bit more in order to get "that fitment", I bet it's not as fast as it looks
1:55 when you decide to build an ugly turbo system instead of going with Fast Intentions, he's making at least 200 less whp than he could be making, then you can't even mount your hood
2:39 The red is fine on this car, but those wheels. It needs to be lowered on race suspension with the wheels spaced out. The chrome wheels look fine but are heavy and boring-shaped.
3:30 That green is unfitting and ugly, plus the nose has a bunch of empty space in the middle. But Murci is an amazing Lambo car.
4:32 This car looks like your neighbor's rusty shitbox to a normal non-car person. Headlights look old and faded. The wheels are your "mainstream JDM choice" and would look far better on Enkei RS05RR or something similar. This car is the true Godzilla, make it look like it too.
4:45 All that front splitter but no wing? So at high speeds it is constantly nose-diving? Still looks like an amazing and fast car...
5:54 The butt of the car is too stubby and short to look aesthetic. Also I can see your wheels are sunk in, again with the spacers! Smh. Good choice with the black wheels though.
6:30 I can already imagine Doug talking over his car and spitting all over the paint while doing it. Lower the car and get rid of those silver wheels.
7:10 Something is wrong with those rear wheels placement and the rear wing. The shape is just out of place. Is the rear bumper missing? And wash it please...
